original_title: L'elevage des poulards de Bresse à Cousance
overview: About poultry: from rearing in 'model farms' to packaging. The film contains footage of a model farm (in the Jura), fattening of the poultry and offering it for sale at the local market, and preparation activities including plucking, tying up wings and legs and packaging.
title: L'elevage des poulards de Bresse à Cousance
